      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The goods for men sold at a haberdasher's shop or store department, such as shirts, ties, socks, belts, hats, gloves. and other accessories. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
